item.title: Best Cops Episodes
item.description: Follow real-life law enforcement officers from various regions and departments of the United States armed with nothing but with cameras to capture their actions, performing their daily duty to serve and protect the public. Cops is an American crime reality tv-series that was first aired in 1989. See the best episodes of Cops below.

item.title: Best Bar Rescue Episodes
item.description: Jon Taffer is the Gordon Ramsay of the bar and nightclub business. In each episode, Taffer helps transform a struggling bar into a vibrant, profitable business, utilizing his expertise as a nightlife consultant. See the best episodes of Bar Rescue below.
